id: FT1
name: Suggesting Pre-Proposals
text: |
  A  Pre-Proposal is a type of entity consisting of a body of text
  and other attributes. A player CAN suggest a Pre-Proposal by
  announcement, specifying its text and an associated title.

  When a Pre-Proposal is suggested, the player that suggested it
  becomes one of the authors of that Pre-Proposal. An author of a
  Pre-Proposal can make another player become an author of that
  Pre-Proposal by announcement.
